Find Your Perfect Peel. Which Strength is Right for You?

Active Peel System is a powerful yet gentle formula ideal for regular use every other day, helping to improve skin tone, texture, and hydration while providing antioxidant protection through botanically derived AHAs, BHAs, and Extremozyme Technology. 

Extra Strength Active Peel Brightening System delivers 3x the exfoliating and brightening power, with a potent blend of six AHAs, exosomes, Snowflake Bulb, and advanced antioxidants to help visibly resurface and brighten the skin’s appearance while providing advanced hydration, minimizing the appearance of fine lines and renewing the look of skin tone and texture. Designed for use 1-2 times per week.

To find out which Active Peel System is right for you, we recommend you consult with an iS Clinical authorized professional. Find one at the link in our bio.
